quran[15]{c,v,t}:
  23,60,"E …ďen okkay…ďe ko …ďe ngokkaa kon, hara …ďer…óe ma…ď…ďe …óen ko hul…óe [Alla], wonan'dema kam…ďe ko fa'ade ka Joomi ma…ď…ďe …ďe nduttoytoo."
  23,61,"∆Āeen [sifaa…ďe …óii sifaaji …óoo] he…ďe yaccoo e mo∆ī∆īereeji …ói, hara kam…ďe ko …ďe adotoo…ďe e majji."
  23,62,"Min pawaani woŇčkii si wonaa fodde baw…óe makki, no ka amen Deftere wowlaynde Goonga kan, hara kam…ďe …ďe too√Īoytaake."
  23,63,"Ko woni, …ďer…óe ma…ď…ďe …óe no e welsungo immorde e …óum, no woodani …ďe kadi golle ga …óuum ko kam…ďe ngollate …óe."
  23,64,"Haa si Min nanngirii neeminaa…ďe ma…ď…ďe …ďen Lepte …óen njaka yoo kam…ďe he…ďe haaca."
  23,65,"Wata on haacu hannde, pellet onon, on wallataake immorde e amen."
  23,66,"GooŇč…óii Aayeeje Amen …óen no janngee e taweede moo…óon, laati…óon ho…óon nduttoo e dow codduli moo…óon."
  23,67,"Ko on mawnintinii…ďe sabu [jeyeede makka] ho…óon kiira haalde bon…ói."
  23,68,"Enee, teskaaki konngol ngol, kaa hara ar e ma…ď…ďe ko araani e baabiraa…ďe ma…ď…ďe adinoo…ďe …ďe?"
  23,69,"Kaa …ďe nganndaani Nulaa…óo ma…ď…ďe on, hara kam…ďe ko …ďe faaytu…ďe mo?"
  23,70,"Kaa hara …ďe mb'ay feetere no e makko? Ko woni, o addanii …ďe Goonga kan …ďur…ďe heewde e ma…ď…ďe ko a√Ī…ďe Goonga kan."
  23,71,"Sinndo Alqur'aana jokkuno belee…óe ma…ď…ďe …óen, kammuuji …óin e leydi ndin bonayno e …ďen wonu…ďe e majji, ko woni, Min addanii…ďe waaju ma…ď…ďe ngun, kam…ďe ko…ďe …óurnii…ďe ga waaju ma…ď…ďe ngun."
  23,72,"Kaa a tori …ďe njeenaari? [Awa] ko njeenaari Joomi maa…óa ndin …ďuri mo∆ī∆īude, ko KaŇčko woni Mo∆ī∆īo Arsikoowo."
  23,73,"Pellet, an ha…óa noddude fa'ade e Laawol Pocciingol."
  23,74,"E pellet, …ďen …ďe mgooŇč…óinaani Laakara on ko …ďe selu…ďe e Laawol ngol."